      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUPER SEQUIN (7) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (23.14) at this track behind Tumby Bay in a Grade 4/5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Key chance in this line up. CLASSIC TEARS (1) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and two placings from six starts. Was out of the placings last time (18.56) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing fifth and beaten 6 lengths. Can feature with the right run. GREAT CHAT (8) has a terrific record this track and trip with four wins and one placing from five starts. Comes off a (29.50) win last time, scoring by half a length in a Grade 4/5 over 515m at Gosford. Makes strong appeal on best. CURIOUS TEARS (2) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
